('BRAND_POSITIONING: Le brand manifesto (declaration d intention) aligne toute l equipe et communique la mission aux clients.', 'Brand manifesto = aligner equipe + mission clients', 'marketing', 'best_practice', 0.80, 'massive_boost_34', 'system'),
('BRAND_POSITIONING: Le competitor analysis quadrant (leader/challenger/niche/visionnaire) situe la marque dans le marche.', 'Competitor quadrant: leader/challenger/niche/visionnaire', 'marketing', 'best_practice', 0.78, 'massive_boost_34', 'system'),
('AUTOMATION_ADVANCED: Le workflow automation le plus rentable: lead capture → enrichissement → scoring → assignation → nurturing.', 'Auto workflow lead: capture → enrich → score → assign → nurture', 'commercial', 'best_practice', 0.85, 'massive_boost_34', 'system'),
