('PERSONAL_PRODUCTIVITY: Le morning routine (routine matinale structuree) augmente la productivite de la journee de 25%.', 'Morning routine = +25% productivite journee', 'rh', 'insight', 0.78, 'massive_boost_39', 'system'),
